### 1. Barcha notificationlarni ko'rish
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/notifications/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. O'qilmaganlarni ko'rish
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/notifications/?is_read=false
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Bitta notificationni o'qilgan qilish (PATCH)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/notifications/notifications/2/mark-read/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "is_read": true
}

### 4. Hammasini o'qilgan qilish
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/notifications/mark-all-read/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}